---
title: Herby Grilled Chicken Niçoise Salad with Foil-Pouch Thyme Potatoes
description: We took some liberties with the classic salad Niçoise, but worry not, this salad is worthy in its own right. Vibrant red potatoes mingle with traditional components like tomatoes and green beans for an unexpectedly harmonious medley. The entire salad is amped up by an intensely flavourful vinaigrette. Bon appétit!
